    <abstract>
      <t>  This document describes the conference service using Session 
  Initiation Protocol. This document explains a mechanism for 
  initiating, modifying and terminating a SIP based conference 
  session. It also explains procedures for adding and removing
  participants in the conference.
	 </t>
